    <item>
      <title>Coinbase 退出市场七年后重返夏威夷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/coinbase-returns-to-hawaii-seven-years-after-exiting-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过七年的缺席，Coinbase Global Inc. 表示将恢复向夏威夷居民提供加密服务，夏威夷是其唯一没有运营的州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/coinbase-returns-to-hawaii-seven-years-after-exiting-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国汽车工人联合会抓住特朗普赞扬马斯克解雇工人的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uaw-seizes-on-donald-trump-praising-elon-musk-for-firing-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全美汽车工人联合会 (UAW) 猛烈抨击前总统唐纳德·特朗普对埃隆·马斯克对待其公司员工所采取的策略的称赞，并将这些言论转化为反对共和党候选人的信息，称工会将瞄准一个关键的选区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/uaw-seizes-on-donald-trump-praising-elon-musk-for-firing-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 15:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Shein 聘请前欧盟官员加强 IPO 游说工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/shein-hires-former-eu-official-to-bolster-lobbying-as-ipo-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shein 聘请了一位前欧盟高级官员来加强其在该地区的游说力度，并在计划在伦敦股票市场首次亮相之际，对潜在的监管审查采取更积极的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/shein-hires-former-eu-official-to-bolster-lobbying-as-ipo-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 15:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
